title: Diabetes medication adherence, language, glycemic control in Latino patients

title_detail.value: Diabetes medication adherence, language, glycemic control in Latino patients

summary: Newly published research has focused on Latino patients with type 2 diabetes. More than 3.1 million Latinos in the United States have diabetes and require daily medication use.
